603
00:43:10,755 --> 00:43:12,840
What's your problem?

604
00:43:15,468 --> 00:43:16,344
What are you doing?

605
00:43:18,054 --> 00:43:19,388
What?

606
00:43:24,811 --> 00:43:25,812
