You've never been specific about anything.

617
00:44:21,617 --> 00:44:23,786
That's because I'm the one
who sets the direction.

618
00:44:23,870 --> 00:44:25,955
Cut the crap, you prick.

619
00:44:26,038 --> 00:44:27,957
I'm done putting up with your nonsense.

620
00:44:28,583 --> 00:44:30,710
I'll just keep living my life,

621
00:44:31,252 --> 00:44:32,962
true to myself,

622
00:44:34,046 --> 00:44:35,006
and my Korean roots.

623
00:44:36,674 --> 00:44:38,092
Don't look down on that, punks!

624
00:44:38,759 --> 00:44:40,219
There's greatness in it.

625
00:44:40,303 --> 00:44:42,138
-Okay, that greatness--
-Shut up!

626
00:45:01,240 --> 00:45:02,617
It's ready, right?

627
00:45:03,326 --> 00:45:05,494
Shall we dig in?

628
00:45:16,881 --> 00:45:17,798
Go on then.

629
00:45:18,925 --> 00:45:19,800
Sorry?

630
00:45:19,884 --> 00:45:22,053
Wasn't there something you wanted to say?

631
00:45:29,393 --> 00:45:30,311
Well…

632
00:45:31,854 --> 00:45:33,564
What's the secret to your leadership?

633
00:45:33,648 --> 00:45:34,732
What?

634
00:45:34,815 --> 00:45:38,444
I was also a team leader
at headquarters for a long time,

635
00:45:38,527 --> 00:45:41,405
but you know how subordinates
are never on the same page.

636
00:45:41,489 --> 00:45:43,491
They only look out for themselves.

637
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:45,785
You know what I mean, right?

638
00:45:45,868 --> 00:45:46,786
I'm not so sure.

639
00:45:46,869 --> 00:45:50,831
I've noticed that people here
really seem to look up to you.

640
00:45:51,582 --> 00:45:52,500
You think?

641
00:45:52,583 --> 00:45:54,710
Tell me. What's your secret?

642
00:45:54,794 --> 00:45:56,712
Do you just shower them with praise?

643
00:45:56,796 --> 00:45:59,131
And then discipline them
if they're out of line?

644
00:45:59,215 --> 00:46:01,342
-Excuse me?
-I mean…

645
00:46:02,927 --> 00:46:07,223
I was wondering if you have
your own management philosophy.

646
00:46:10,393 --> 00:46:11,310
And if I do?

647
00:46:12,770 --> 00:46:16,357
I was wondering if I could get
a quick tip from you.

648
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:18,359
A quick tip?

649
00:46:25,825 --> 00:46:27,451
First of all,

650
00:46:29,412 --> 00:46:31,622
