when I ask something.

669
00:47:27,470 --> 00:47:29,638
-What would you use my advice for?
-What do you think?

670
00:47:29,722 --> 00:47:33,100
I was going to use it once I became
an executive at headquarters.

671
00:47:33,934 --> 00:47:35,436
You're going back to headquarters?

672
00:47:35,519 --> 00:47:36,896
Of course.

673
00:47:36,979 --> 00:47:39,440
